high_descs: Turn around and walk to the bed.
Pick up the box from the far side of the bed.
Carry the box and turn to around and face the desk on the right, where the lamp is.
Hold the box and turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a box and turn on the lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then turn right again and walk over to the bed.
Pick up the pillow off of the end of the bed.
Walk over to the small lamp on the desk behind you.
Turn on the light of the small lamp on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Examine a pillow in the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the foot of the bed.
Pick up the pillow on the bed.
Turn around and take a step, then face the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a pillow by the light of a lamp.
